Usage of sigmaana 
(0) Prepare merge_$BEAM_C.root and merge_$BEAM_E.root in treefiles
(1) Execute
 ./bin/Batch_Sigma_calc.sh NUCLIDE BEAM LABEL
for example  ./bin/Batch_Sigma_calc.sh "42Ca" "41Ca" "1"
  in sigmaana directory

(2) If you would like to execute multiple calculation 
./bin/Multi_Sigma_calc_$BEAM.sh LABEL 

[option]
When you prepare spe_NUCLIDE_BEAM_C.root and spe_NUCLIDE_BEAM_E.root
you can use  ./bin/Batch_Sigma_calc_spe.sh NUCLIDE BEAM LABEL
